  <p>The <a href="/alfa-laval-mab-centrifuge/">Alfa Laval MAB</a>-102 is the smallest <a href="/disc-stack-centrifuge/">disc-stack centrifuge</a>. This centrifuge has a bowl speed of <strong>9,300 RPM</strong> that exerts a g-force of <strong>over 8,000 Gs.</strong> It is a three-phase, manual clean type centrifuge that can separate oil, water, and small amounts of solid sludge.</p>

  <p>This centrifuge is perfect for small boats and generators to polish the diesel fuel to ensure reliable engine operation.</p>

  <p>Alfa Laval AB (Sweden) is the manufacturer of the MAB-102 disc stack centrifuge. Dolphin Centrifuge's equivalent model for this platform is the DMPX-005, available through our <a href="/contact-for-alfa-laval-centrifuges/">sales and quoting team</a>.</p>

